content.p: Assistant Professor, Dr. Wong obtained his Master of Engineering with Honours in Civil Engineering from University of Nottingham Malaysia Campus. He then pursued a Doctor of Philosophy degree in Civil Engineering at the same University since September 2014. His research interests include Numerical Modelling and Advanced Triaxial Testing.
